name: Googlers Magisk Repo
description: A collection of handy tools and tweaks for your Magisk-enabled Android device. If you're into customizing your phone, GMR makes it easy to find, download, and install Magisk modules that can enhance your device's functionality or add cool features.

modules.name: BetterKnownInstalled (BKI)

modules.description: Patching (installer, installerUid, installInitiator, installOriginator) in packages.xml and cleaning packages-warnings.xml for defeating DroidGuard: UNKNOWN_INSTALLED

note.message: Installation from recovery is not supported. You must install this module from within a running Android environment (Magisk/KernelSU/APatch)
note.title: Important!
